column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid, p.ra,p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,   s.class AS type, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r,   p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, s.z AS Redshift FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   p.modelMag_r BETWEEN # AND #  AND s.z BETWEEN # AND #
